        <mxCell id="JMq97p6jJsFnZODxczWG-134" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional Requriements" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="150" width="420" x="-80" y="-640" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="JMq97p6jJsFnZODxczWG-135" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1.Users should be able to login&amp;nbsp; using their username and Password&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;2.Users should be able to Follow other users&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 3.Users should be able to like and cooments on different Posts&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.Users should be able to Post&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;5.Users should be able to see their following&#39;s&amp;nbsp; and followers post on their feed&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="80" width="270" x="40" y="-510" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="JMq97p6jJsFnZODxczWG-136" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Non Functional Requriements&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Platform must be able to handle 1M DAU&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Low latency for getting the feed ~10ms&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3.Platform should have EVENTUAL CONCISTENCY&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4.Platform should have minimal downtime&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="200" width="570" x="-85" y="-430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="JMq97p6jJsFnZODxczWG-137" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="API DESIGN&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Login:&amp;nbsp; POST:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;/user/login&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RequestBody: {Username.Password}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Response: {JwtToken&amp;nbsp; / Unauthorized}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Feed GET: /user/feed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RequestBody{JwtToken}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Response:{Post MetaData + Video/Image}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Add&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Post&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; : Post&amp;nbsp; : /user./post&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RequestBody:{JwtToken +Post MetaData + Image/Video}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Response:{ResponseEntity with Warning/Sucess Message}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Like:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Post&amp;nbsp; /user/like/post_id=?&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RequestBody:{JwtToken + postd)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Response:{ResponseEntity}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Comment: Post /user/comment/postid=?&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RequestBody:{JwtToken+postID+Comment}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Response:{ResponseEntity}&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="470" width="580" x="630" y="-610" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
